This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=5261

Executes a command on `BufWritePost` events. E.g.:
'!:exe [so %]' sources the file on each save.

Defaults: exe, md, sass, less, jade, coffee.
!::exe [expression] : executes expression.
!::md [dir] : outputs file.html in dir. (default = file's dir )

More detailed overview:
https://github.com/romgrk/vim-exeline
